rows.label: qst702406_msg0002
rows.name: Uh? Do I want to join the militia?

rows.label: qst702406_msg0003
rows.name:
No. Sorry, you're outta
luck there, mate.

rows.label: qst702406_msg0004
rows.name:
And anyway, I've got business in
this town that needs attending.
Hope you find someone, though!

rows.label: qst702406_msg0005
rows.name:
Hrm? I could bring skills
that few others could?

rows.label: qst702406_msg0006
rows.name:
All right, all right. Since
you put it that way... I guess
I can't brush you off.

rows.label: qst702406_msg0007
rows.name:
Go on then. I'll consider it at
least. But don't hold your breath.

rows.label: qst702406_msg0101
rows.name:
Fine, fine. Your passion
really struck a chord with
me. I'll think it through.

rows.label: qst702406_msg0102
rows.name:
In the unlikely scenario
that I do decide to sign
up, I'll head to the camp.

rows.label: qst702406_msg0103
rows.name: But honestly, don't hold your breath.
